          "id": "mobile_faq_2",
          "type": "faq_item",
          "name": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will I actually get credit for sales that come through this app?",
            "answer": "Yes, guaranteed. Every link you share through the app is automatically connected to your rep ID through FairShare™ attribution. Even if someone clicks your link, waits three weeks, and buys after finding the company through Google, you still get full credit. No codes to remember, no spreadsheets to track—just automatic, reliable attribution."
